        <p class="text-[#E5E7EB] font-['Inter_Variable'] text-base mb-8">
          With a Bachelor of Science in New Media Interactive Development from
          the Rochester Institute of Technology and nearly 3 years of experience
          as a front-end developer, I bring both technical knowledge and a
          passion for problem-solving to every project. I love transforming
          ideas from simple wireframes and mock-ups into clean, accessible
          user-friendly interfaces.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#E5E7EB] font-['Inter_Variable'] text-base mb-8">
          I'm a firm believer that beautiful design and a seamless user
          experience are crucial for any successful application. My mission is
          to ensure that the needs of the users are met, while also delivering a
          product that is both functional and visually appealing.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#E5E7EB] font-['Inter_Variable'] text-base mb-8">
          Currently, I am a Front-End Developer at <a
            href='https://linksquares.com/'
