            class='text-[#BB96EA] hover:underline'>LinkSquares</a
          >, where I am constantly collaborating cross-functionally with
          designers, product managers, and other engineers to build interfaces
          that simultaneously provide the highest quality user experience and
          align with the goals of the business and our products.
        </p>
